social_posts.post_text: First girls day post baby. (Immediately naps following photo 😂)
Today I got to cast for my dream company, so excited and blessed to be requested, thank you to the best agency for working with me every stage of my life 🩵 (swipe for the cutest bts ever)
Motherhood 💕the greatest joy in my life, I love these girls so much, and am so thankful for all they give me 🤍
My sweet Violet 💜 I can’t believe you’re already ONE! You fill us with so much joy and made our little family complete, we love you our little flower baby ✨Happy Birthday V

And just like that, our house became a home 🤍

The last few weeks have been nonstop craziness as we’ve tried to move into our new space and new neighborhood. Letting go of the past, and remaining open and earnest for what’s to come. Life changes, but family remains. ❤️

Such an amazing weekend getting to spend it with such amazing women! One of my favorite things about my career as a model/actress in Miami are the beautiful friendships I’ve made, I’ll always be thankful for these girls and am so happy to support such amazing women owned businesses 💛 @xcviofficial @ogeventsla
When someone says I train like a girl. I say “Omg thank you!!!” @destiny_jones555

Hubby appreciation post ❤️ 
It’s so amazing how far our love has taken us. From two models living in South Beach to a full family of four. You are the most amazing dad these girls could ever dream of, and my heart bursts with joy and excitement for all the many adventures to come ✨

Growing up my Aunt Laura would take all five of us siblings to Disney, when we tragically lost her to cancer we said we would take the kids to carry on the tradition. 10 adults, 9 grandkids, and a lifetime of memories ❤️ Aunt Laura we felt you every step of the way, you are and always will be in our hearts ✨

Yesterday was a busy day (like always) trying to run errands with the girls, get 100 things ticked off the to do list. As we drove we noticed a little Farm. We had passed it before, always meaning to go one day. I looked at Karl, and smiled saying today’s the day. We put all else aside and jst said yes. Well let me tell you, it was worth it 💛
